<p>Usually,&#xA0;Salesforce&#xA0;shows a special&#xA0;list view&#xA0;called&#xA0;Recently Viewed. You can&#xA0;create and customize&#xA0;a&#xA0;new&#xA0;List View&#xA0;by&#xA0;<strong>clicking the&#xA0;gear icon</strong>, then <strong>in a&#xA0;dropdown menu, choose New</strong>.</p>
